Today is a different morning for Kiss FM listeners as they were greeted with a new voice. Media personality Felix Odiwuor popularly known as Jalang'o has officially joined the Kiss FM family. He will be working alongside Kamene Goro every weekday morning from 6 am to 10 am. "East or West, Home is Best.Kiss Family, help us welcome," Kiss FM posted on Instagram. Kamene previously hosted the Morning Kiss with Andrew Kibe. This is not the first time for Jalang'o to host a radio show as he has been a radio presenter for years and has even worked with Caroline Mutoko when she was a Kiss FM presenter.